evaluation

Class EvaluationResultsSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • evaluation.EvaluationResultsSummary

  • public class EvaluationResultsSummary
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which summarizes the EvaluationResults of multiple evaluations. If you run multiple evaluations with the same collectors and you want to combine the results of the evaluations you can use this class. This class simple computes the averaged values and the standard deviation for each specific collector and their measures by only adding the EvaluationResults of each run.
    Author:
    MK
